{"tid":1468521,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"請記住癱瘓機場係為咗還眼","createTime":"2019-08-13T19:03:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T19:23:31.000Z","uid":258972,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4676b4643091eb4405520b27172d4525642d057c","tid":1468521,"uid":258972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:03:24.000Z","msg":"你可以道歉派糖<br />\n但癱瘓機場本身就係宜家運動weekday主軸<br />\n一定要做無得讓<br />\n<br />\n禁制令一出<br />\n意味住要好禮拜一咁多人先可以work.<br />\n學生唔該盡出<br />\n唔好搞ocamp<br />\n<br />\n因此捉鬼唔係重點<br />\n係癱機場"},{"pid":"59bdea67f73d4f780bdf4295718e5b5c563feb87","tid":1468521,"uid":258972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:03:35.000Z","msg":"自push"},{"pid":"70308fbb6ce2dccdd8985412ceac5c2a81432ca8","tid":1468521,"uid":258972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:03:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"816bf3b83cb0c8b66c2069429d363637673f703e","tid":1468521,"uid":258972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:04:02.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"6a396039830cd4fbc20097d6624ed60a85843fa5","tid":1468521,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:04:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">絕不割蓆，唯要改進</span><br />\n<br />\n我地唔會割蓆，但我地亦都會持續去改進，希望運動可以更上一層樓邁向成功之日，我地要一齊尊重，正如人人平等冇話邊個大啲有得話事啲，有咩建議大家投票解決，我地亦要每日一齊去檢討得失，正如人人都會有失誤嘅時候<br />\n<br />\n古今中外所以社會運動總會有失誤嘅時候，可貴之處就係識得自省，而呢場運動其中一樣重要嘅係自己要有一個自省精神，一旦出現失誤就要認，認完就要反省，吸取教訓，下次再可以做好啲，人數亦會keep住多，人多就可以贏<br />\n<br />\n如果出現失誤唔去承認，唔去反省，唔尊重對方互相指罵，只會不斷重複失誤，人數會變少，最後重演2014年雨革失敗歷史。"},{"pid":"530674a11562f08f59580c1b74f59d6d055810f1","tid":1468521,"uid":258972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:04:12.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"f2efeec88b09cf35ddbce996f7f192db7e3f9810","tid":1468521,"uid":258972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:04:28.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a91185d25c4d613da066ad332c6c142c7ee27754","tid":1468521,"uid":258972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:04:42.000Z","msg":"pishhhhhhh"},{"pid":"1eebf60ca34924603530bb5ac5765a99ad74a9e9","tid":1468521,"uid":258972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:06:32.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"d5b4b7bf3dbdab01609a99b1237d09e90ef4e5b8","tid":1468521,"uid":258972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:06:48.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"fdf2c716effe97595480e70a5ceeca15f8be6741","tid":1468521,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:08:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fd9c9740700a81c7810ff0acc488064dff3eea58","tid":1468521,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:09:42.000Z","msg":"禁制令係禁制示威者 冇話唔比人去機場涼冷氣<br />\n唔叫口號 單純去涼冷氣 你奈我咩何<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個唔覺意 出面太熱 太多人去窒爆機場"},{"pid":"3eedb8ea0b75a51574cd0c52c28c47404f1cfedd","tid":1468521,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:10:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a63b91d95809eed3aebe67f9eaca97c1d0b81d12","tid":1468521,"uid":258972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:10:41.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"63f495c86b4a0597610e14f7850c93bc211f5996","tid":1468521,"uid":258972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:11:44.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"ab2b9900efca55e3e6e05d7dae39af3640cab0dc","tid":1468521,"uid":258972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:14:08.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n唔L好去剩道歉"},{"pid":"853085140c0e471aa8f1809b9d5f13d0b5145aec","tid":1468521,"uid":258972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd9c9740700a81c7810ff0acc488064dff3eea58","tid":1468521,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:09:42.000Z","msg":"禁制令係禁制示威者 冇話唔比人去機場涼冷氣<br />\n唔叫口號 單純去涼冷氣 你奈我咩何<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.g